---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Low-cost prescription drugs — Buddy" description="Safe, evidence-backed, low-cost prescription drug options. Coming soon.">

<section class="stub-hero">
  <div class="stub-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">AIIT-THRESI · Forthcoming</div>
    <h1>Low-cost drugs.</h1>
    <p class="stub-sub">A reference for the cheap, safe, often-overlooked prescription drugs that actually work — backed by real trials, not marketing budgets.</p>

    <div class="stub-card">
      <div class="stub-card-label">Status</div>
      <div class="stub-card-body">
        <p>Compiling. Criteria: must be (a) prescribable in the US today, (b) off-patent or generic, (c) backed by peer-reviewed efficacy evidence, (d) under $50/month cash price for a standard course.</p>
        <p>If you have a drug you think belongs on this list, send it with the citation. We're not publishing anything without the paper behind it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stub-actions">
      <a href="/save-lives" class="stub-cta">Read Save Lives Now →</a>
      <a href="mailto:reliablerestaurantrepair@gmail.com?subject=Low-cost%20drug%20submission" class="stub-cta-ghost">Submit a drug</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .stub-hero {
    padding: 160px 24px 120px;
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center top, rgba(64,192,176,0.05) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }
  .stub-inner { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .stub-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(56px, 10vw, 120px);
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 16px 0 32px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .stub-sub {
    color: var(--muted-hi);
    font-size: clamp(17px, 2.2vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }
  .stub-card {
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 44px;
    border: 1px solid var(--edge);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    background: rgba(10,10,18,0.4);
  }
  .stub-card-label {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--amber);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .stub-card-body p {
    color: var(--ink); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }
  .stub-card-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .stub-actions {
    display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .stub-cta, .stub-cta-ghost {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 11pt; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 16px 30px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.25s, color 0.25s, border-color 0.25s;
  }
  .stub-cta {
    color: var(--amber);
    border: 1px solid var(--amber);
  }
  .stub-cta:hover { background: var(--amber); color: #0a0a12; }
  .stub-cta-ghost {
    color: var(--muted-hi);
    border: 1px solid var(--edge);
  }
  .stub-cta-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--amber); color: var(--amber); }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .stub-hero { padding: 120px 20px 80px; }
    .stub-card { padding: 22px 22px; }
  }
</style>

</Layout>
